text_annotations.text: * Flash ~{CS} pullup may not be\n  necessary depending on flash chip

* Make sure R6 & R7 are close to pins 46 & 47 (USB D- & D+)
* 1kΩ resistor on TMC UART TX per TMC2209 datasheet Figure 4.1
* ACT_LED can be re-assigned to any free pin
* Check RP2040 pin mux before re-assigning UART & I2C pins
* Crystal requires extra start up time
* Make sure 1u caps are close to pin 44 (VREG_IN) & 45 (VREG_OUT)
